title: Samuel L. Ipsum
content: Well, the way they make shows is, they make one show. That show's called a pilot. Then they show that show to the people who make shows, and on the strength of that one show they decide if they're going to make more shows. Some pilots get picked and become television programs. Some don't, become nothing. She starred in one of the ones that became nothing. You read the Bible, Ringo? You see there's this passage I got memorized, Ezekial 25:17, the path of the righteous man is beset on all sides by in the iniquities of the selfish and the tyranny of evil men...
